00:26:08.740 --> 00:26:11.380
So let's pause for
just a second here.

00:26:11.380 --> 00:26:13.710
So when I multiply
all of this out,

00:26:13.710 --> 00:26:16.560
I'm going to get one term
that involves background

00:26:16.560 --> 00:26:20.080
inverse metric hitting all the
derivatives of my background

00:26:20.080 --> 00:26:20.580
metric.

00:26:27.050 --> 00:26:28.720
I'm going to call it--

00:26:28.720 --> 00:26:32.730
