00:28:40.210 --> 00:28:45.140
symbols, but only acting
on the h's and using

00:28:45.140 --> 00:28:49.023
covariant derivatives rather
than partial derivatives.

00:28:53.347 --> 00:28:55.680
I don't have a good way to
